'''Grahrk''' was a surname used by several [[Devaronian/Legends|Devaronians]].
*'''[[Vilmarh Grahrk]]''', a notorious mercenary, smuggler, and gambler, who worked with [[Quinlan Vos/Legends|Quinlan Vos]] upon occasion.
*'''[[Holmar Grahrk]]''', a mercenary who often worked with his cousin Vilmarh.
*'''[[Olmar Grahrk]]''', Holmar's son, who worked with his relatives during the Yinchorri crisis.
*'''[[Dvakvar Grahrk]]''', a [[Jedi Knight/Legends|Jedi Knight]] during the [[Jedi Civil War]]. {{C|Non-canon cut content}}

